  Text: |
    Slide 12.  Asset Library 
    [Show Comparison Unity Asset Store - Asset Library]
    
    > Let’s switch some gears, we went through the hard part. 
    
    > From now on it will be a lot easier here. 
    
    > Think of the Asset Library as a “Unity Editor-Integrated Asset Store and Package Manager”
    This is the place where you can start downloading content to enrich your lenses and it’s for Free. 
    
    > You can verify if the package are installed correctly with the label on the package 
    
    > You also can update the packages in place, very similarly from the package manager in unity. 

